        <title>Hello World</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;To kick this blog off I thought Iâ€™d make a Hello World post. Since learning any new programming language typically begins with making a simple Hello World program this seems appropriate.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is a simple Hello World program using css animation.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;helloworld-container&quot;&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;helloworld-box&quot;&gt;
